have global responsibilities for procurement transportation continuous improvement sustainability and quality safety and regulatory operations labour relations and workforce issues across product supply will also be coordinated at a global level she is also expected to lead the company’s global supply chain council which will be comprised of supply chain leaders from across the globe and will build the next generation of supply chain capability at the company kc said in a press release macquillan has extensive experience in procurement technology and engineering and has lived and worked in russia europe and dubai in the united arab emirates most recently she was responsible for manufacturing engineering and logistics for the global petcare business a us billion business for mars macquillan will report to thomas falk chairman and ceo and become a member of kc’s global senior leadership team falk said “this appointment demonstrates our commitment to drive further cost transformation and increased effectiveness across our supply chain sandra brings a wealth of global experience to this new position on our senior team i’m confident that she will help us improve the value we can deliver from a truly world class supply chain operation” every day nearly a quarter of the worlds population trust kcs brands and the solutions they provide to enhance their health hygiene and wellbeing with brands such as kleenex scott huggies pullups kotex and depend kimberlyclark holds no  or no  share positions in more than  countries gk fibrefashion news desk  india     advertisements           category news agro textiles automobile textiles clothing textiles composites construction textiles geo textiles hometech textiles industrial textiles machinery medical textiles nonwoven oekotech textiles packaging textiles protective textile raw material sports textiles tradefairs esteemed clients                                                                            disclaimer  about us  sitemap 